FBIS4-22122 "jptot017__l94061" JPRS-TOT-94-017-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 25 April 1994 WEST EUROPE GREECE ELA Claims UN Building Bomb; Second Device Found; New Blast ELA Claims UN Building Bomb; Second Device Found; New Blast NC2504052594 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 0400 GMT 25 Apr 94 NC2504052594 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Greek BFN [Text] ELA [Revolutionary People's Struggle] called the newspaper ELEVTHEROTIPIA at 0340 [0040 GMT] today. An hour later, a homemade device was discovered at the entrance to the UN High Commission building on the corner of Zoodhokhou Piyis and Arakhovis Streets. Another bomb exploded at the same building yesterday morning. Police bomb experts dismantled the device. Another bomb exploded at 0445 [0145 GMT] today at the corner of Ayios Meletios and Filis Streets under the car of [words indistinct] security. The device, which emitted various gases, destroyed the car.
